<plot>Documentary about Danish communists who were put in the Stutthof Concentration Camp during the German occupation of Denmark in WWII. The widows to these men, nicknamed "The Red Widows" formed the "Stutthof Committee" and helped Red Cross bring food and supplies to the prisoners. Thanks to the Committee thousands survived Stutthof.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?519368</url></doc>
